public interface NameValueList

Represents a list of name-value pairs, or entries. Typically, NameValueList is used to get WorkItem or Document attributes.

void addNameValue(java.lang.String name,
                  java.lang.String value)
Adds a new entry with the specified name and value to the NameValueList. This operation is optional. If the list previously contained an entry for this name, replaces the old value with the specified value.

name - The name of the entry.
